import React from 'react'
import {
    SideBarContainer,
    Icon,
    CloseIcon
} from './SideBarElements';

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <>
          <SideBarContainer>
              <Icon>
                  <CloseIcon />
              </Icon>
              <SidebarWrapper>
                  <SidebarMenu>
                      <SidebarLink to="about">
                          About
                      </SidebarLink>
                  </SidebarMenu>
              </SidebarWrapper>
          </SideBarContainer>  
        </>
    )
}

export default Sidebar
